the 63 and earlier bus es use the same sunroof handle as a bug, and that bug 
handle can also fit on a 64-67.   I suggest cross referencing parts lists on 
the other parts.   I dont think they fit though, rails diff sahpe, cross pieces 
wider on a bus.  But do check.
